    "author_association": "CONTRIBUTOR",
    "body": "Hey, we found where the issue is. The error happens because we build our files in ES5, not in ES3. \r\n\r\nSteps you need to take to transform our code into ES3:\r\n\r\n1. install babel\r\n2. add the plugins: `'babel-plugin-transform-es3-property-literals', 'babel-plugin-transform-es3-member-expression-literals', '@babel/plugin-transform-reserved-words',`\r\n3. run babel on InstantSearch\r\n\r\nThen only after that, YUI compressor will be happy and work.",
