    "author_association": "CONTRIBUTOR",
    "body": "Easiest route: give up on trying to minify with YUI, find some way to disable it, since our source is already minified. Maybe it won't be minified if you load it via CDN for example. \r\n\r\nI'll close this issue now, since I don't see a working solution or reason to use YUI compressor. \r\n\r\nThanks, please still get back to give more info if you got it to work some way",
